## Highest priority

### 1. Supplement tracking
This is now the top near-term feature area.

Focus now:
- add dedicated supplement tracking section/flow
- make supplement logging lightweight and quick
- support supplement name, dose/amount, time taken, optional notes
- keep supplement tracking distinct enough from food logging to stay clear
- design it so optional reminder/alarm support can be added later without ripping it apart
- keep the logging flow fast enough to use daily without becoming another annoying ritual humans invent for themselves

### 2. Calorie + electrolyte truth pass
These belong together now because they both affect whether the app tells the truth about the day instead of making pretty lies.

Focus now:
